item.title: Do Yeong Kang
item.description: Do Yeong Kang is a undergraduated research intern in Effective Learning Algorithms (ELA) group. He is interested in research on Hyper-Dimensional Computing (HDC) and Vector Symbolic Architectures (VSA) that are known for providing more efficient learning than conventional learning models. Education B.S. in Mathematics B.S. in Electronic and Electrical Engineering

item.title: Hee Sung Jeong
item.description: Hee Sung Jeong is an undergraduate student in the School of Electronic and Electrical Engineering at SungKyunKwan University. Her research focuses on design of energy-efficient hardware and algorithms for Processing-in-Memory(PIM).
